Steps.Message: Update at 11:17 - Our engineers are on their way. At this point we think the issue is an overhead fault that initially interrupted power to 1819 properties. However, by rerouting electricity in the area, currently 118 customers are still affected. Using an average timescale, we're estimating power will be on between 12:30 and 13:30, but this may change later. Power back on? To stop receiving texts, please just send CANCEL to 80876 (standard text fees apply).

We became aware of this power cut at 11:07. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
